item.title: Gentlemen Dress
item.dc:creator: cumulo
item.content:encoded:
HBDesign designs Men's Suits for more exquisite life. Please check our Size Chart before choosing our products to fit your figure well. Absolutely alterations is required for your Suit to fit perfect, please contact your local tailor's shop for help. We also support tailor made to fit you figure better. Please contact us for more details. Please bear in mind that the color of our products displays on each LCD monitors will be different depend on the setting of your LCD monitors and the angle to see. Warranty Quality is our highest priority at HBDesign. If you feel that a suit is damaged due to a manufacturing defect, please contact us for details on how to exchange the product. Returned products are inspected by our Quality Team and replaced if the damage is the result of a manufacturing defect and not caused by misuse or activities other than the intended purpose. If the same style and size are not available, a substitute replacement of comparable value will be given.
Return Policy
Within 15 days if you are not completely satisfied with your purchase, return it for a full refund or exchange. If you are missing your return label, please contact us, we will be happy to assist you. Any item that is returned that does not meet our inspection and evaluation from our Quality Team will not be eligible for a return. Items must be free of: dirt, odors (i.e. cigarette, sweat, detergent, any sports medication, etc), animal dander, deodorant marks, and any visible signs of wear and tear. P.S. Any return will be charged at least $15 for freight.

item.title: Leather Pursue
item.dc:creator: cumulo
item.content:encoded: Ideal for daily use, this sling bag is best to carry various food items and medicines especially when you are planning a trip with your family. Designed in the collection house of Caprese, it will surely bring a graceful touch in your attire. Featuring stylish exterior and defined edges, this designer piece comes up with multiple slots to keep your essentials and plastic money with an ultimate ease. Moreover, it has a zipper pocket at the back, an inside pocket for coins and embossed logo of the brand to be an instant grab. Get large number of compliments for your elegant choice as it is a long lasting product.

item.title: Kids Shirts Set
item.dc:creator: cumulo
item.content:encoded: Full sleeves formal shirt with two chest pockets and front closure. Green thread used on the pockets and the slogan on it gives it a trend in itself.

item.title: Leather Bag
item.dc:creator: cumulo
item.content:encoded: Style, meet substance. Streamlined, simple and logo-free, this fresh take on a traditional bucket bag has both a single top strap (perfect for slinging in the crook of your arm) and a crossbody option. Bonus: a cool little luggage tag (complete with our signature collar stud closure).

item.title: Trendy Winter Jacket for Men
item.dc:creator: cumulo
item.content:encoded:
A simple design that packs serious punch, this wool-blend jacket from Dockers features four front pockets for convenient on-the-go storage.
Stand collar; interior knit trim Zip front with hidden snap-placket overlay Epaulets at shoulders Long sleeves with buttoned cuffs Four buttoned flap pockets at front (two at chest; two at waist) Lined Shell: wool/polyester/rayon/other fiber; Lining and fill: polyester; Knit trim: acrylic Dry clean Imported
item.excerpt:encoded: This rugged, fleece-lined jacket made of a cotton-blend, water-resistant canvas features dual-entry pockets and is the perfect jacket for fall and spring-like weather conditions.

item.title: Formal Suit for Men
item.dc:creator: cumulo
item.content:encoded:
The ultimate in elegant style and superior quality. Tailored in Superfine wool with Bemberg lining and grosgrain satin lapels and buttons. Single breasted, peak lapel jacket with one button closure.
Unvented and fully lined. Single-pleat trousers with grosgrain satin stripe, half lined to the knee. Unfinished bottoms for altering ease.
Dry clean.
Imported.
item.excerpt:encoded: A must-have in your party wear collection is this pack of two black coloured suits from Hangrr. Lending you a smart and classy look, these suits are worth investing in. Made from poly wool, these slim-fit suits will keep you at ease all day long.
